  <data name="BtnReset.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Immediately halts and safely resets Grbl without a power-cycle.
Accepts and executes this command at any time.
If reset while in motion, Grbl will throw an alarm to indicate position may be lost from the motion halt.
If reset while not in motion, position is retained and re-homing is not required.</value>
